Title: Amplitude Zeroes in Collinear Processes or What Is Left from a

Factorizable 2d Model in Higher DimensionsAuthors: G. Gat and B. Rosenstein

Comments: latex , 8 pp., 2 fig. not included

Journal-ref: Phys. Lett. B312 (1993) 129-132

We show that for collinear processes, i.e. processes where the incoming andoutgoing momenta are aligned along the same line, the S-matrix of the treeproduct of $2\rightarrow 2$ elements. In particular this means nullification ofall collinear $2 \rightarrow n$ amplitudes for $n > 2$.